[{"index": 0, "text": "like what was like the hardest thing for y 'all when you think back?", "start": 0.43, "end": 3.931, "zh": "回想起来，你们觉得最难的是什么？", "zh_hant": "回想起來，你們覺得最難的是什麼？"}, {"index": 1, "text": "What was like the biggest culture shock?", "start": 3.531, "end": 5.391, "zh": "最大的文化冲击是什么？", "zh_hant": "最大的文化衝擊是什麼？"}, {"index": 2, "text": "Or what was like one of the hardest things?", "start": 5.171, "end": 7.352, "zh": "或者说最难的事情之一是什么？", "zh_hant": "或者說最難的事情之一是什麼？"}, {"index": 3, "text": "Or was there ever a moment where you said something that was like the wrong word in the worst way?", "start": 7.952, "end": 13.773, "zh": "有没有那种你说错话说得特别糟糕的时刻？", "zh_hant": "有沒有那種你說錯話說得特別糟糕的時刻？"}, {"index": 4, "text": "Yeah, because you know Korean…", "start": 13.833, "end": 16.734, "zh": "对，因为你知道韩语……", "zh_hant": "對，因為你知道韓語……"}, {"index": 5, "text": "It has a lot of like Hanzha.", "start": 17.634, "end": 19.475, "zh": "里面有很多汉字词。", "zh_hant": "裡面有很多漢字詞。"}, {"index": 6, "text": "It's a word that came from like Chinese something.", "start": 19.895, "end": 23.435, "zh": "这个词其实是从中文之类的语言来的。", "zh_hant": "這個詞其實是從中文之類的語言來的。"}, {"index": 7, "text": "So I just mix them up a lot when I first time in Korea.", "start": 23.236, "end": 27.256, "zh": "所以我刚到韩国的时候经常把它们搞混。", "zh_hant": "所以我剛到韓國的時候經常把它們搞混。"}, {"index": 8, "text": "But actually the…", "start": 27.297, "end": 28.717, "zh": "但其实……", "zh_hant": "但其實……"}, {"index": 9, "text": "You were talking about the culture shock.", "start": 29.657, "end": 31.777, "zh": "你刚才说到文化冲击。", "zh_hant": "你剛才說到文化衝擊。"}, {"index": 10, "text": "It's super different from I think from between China and Korea.", "start": 32.198, "end": 36.739, "zh": "我觉得中国和韩国之间真的很不一样。", "zh_hant": "我覺得中國和韓國之間真的很不一樣。"}, {"index": 11, "text": "Because you know in our country…", "start": 36.339, "end": 38.539, "zh": "因为在我们国家……", "zh_hant": "因為在我們國家……"}, {"index": 12, "text": "The like…", "start": 38.459, "end": 39.579, "zh": "就是那种……", "zh_hant": "就是那種……"}, {"index": 13, "text": "Unnie, dongsaeng…", "start": 39.619, "end": 41.24, "zh": "unnie、dongsaeng这种称呼……", "zh_hant": "unnie、dongsaeng這種稱呼……"}, {"index": 14, "text": "We don't have these things.", "start": 42.3, "end": 43.88, "zh": "我们没有这些东西。", "zh_hant": "我們沒有這些東西。"}, {"index": 15, "text": "So…", "start": 43.48, "end": 44.08, "zh": "所以……", "zh_hant": "所以……"}, {"index": 16, "text": "And for me, my personality…", "start": 44.241, "end": 46.141, "zh": "而且对我来说，我的性格……", "zh_hant": "而且對我來說，我的性格……"}, {"index": 17, "text": "I'm really you know outgoing and I just see everybody as my friends.", "start": 45.901, "end": 50.362, "zh": "我真的很外向，我看每个人都是朋友。", "zh_hant": "我真的很外向，我看每個人都是朋友。"}, {"index": 18, "text": "So I don't like like…", "start": 50.082, "end": 51.342, "zh": "所以我不太喜欢……", "zh_hant": "所以我不太喜歡……"}, {"index": 19, "text": "Oh I have to listen to the sisters sometimes.", "start": 50.942, "end": 54.103, "zh": "哦，有时候还得听姐姐们的话。", "zh_hant": "哦，有時候還得聽姐姐們的話。"}, {"index": 20, "text": "So very first time, I just couldn't receive that.", "start": 54.203, "end": 58.564, "zh": "所以一开始我完全接受不了。", "zh_hant": "所以一開始我完全接受不了。"}, {"index": 21, "text": "Because the SINGEI team, they asked me to…", "start": 58.164, "end": 60.964, "zh": "因为SINGEI的团队让我……", "zh_hant": "因為SINGEI的團隊讓我……"}, {"index": 22, "text": "You have to listen to unnies.", "start": 60.604, "end": 63.405, "zh": "说你必须听unnie们的话。", "zh_hant": "說你必須聽unnie們的話。"}, {"index": 23, "text": "Sunbae.", "start": 63.005, "end": 63.905, "zh": "还有sunbae。", "zh_hant": "還有sunbae。"}, {"index": 24, "text": "I was like, why?", "start": 63.605, "end": 65.485, "zh": "我当时就想，为什么？", "zh_hant": "我當時就想，為什麼？"}, {"index": 25, "text": "do I have to do it?", "start": 65.306, "end": 67.306, "zh": "我为什么要这样做？", "zh_hant": "我為什麼要這樣做？"}, {"index": 26, "text": "Because I have my own personality.", "start": 66.906, "end": 69.006, "zh": "因为我有自己的个性。", "zh_hant": "因為我有自己的個性。"}, {"index": 27, "text": "I'm Wookie.", "start": 68.726, "end": 70.007, "zh": "我是Wookie。", "zh_hant": "我是Wookie。"}, {"index": 28, "text": "But why I have to…", "start": 70.167, "end": 71.427, "zh": "但为什么我非得……", "zh_hant": "但為什麼我非得……"}, {"index": 29, "text": "Because I lived in my hometown for about 20 years.", "start": 71.027, "end": 76.788, "zh": "因为我在我家乡生活了差不多20年。", "zh_hant": "因為我在我家鄉生活了差不多20年。"}, {"index": 30, "text": "But now you ask me to change it?", "start": 76.388, "end": 79.289, "zh": "结果现在你让我改？", "zh_hant": "結果現在你讓我改？"}, {"index": 31, "text": "I said, no.", "start": 78.889, "end": 79.449, "zh": "我说，不。", "zh_hant": "我說，不。"}, {"index": 32, "text": "I won't do it.", "start": 79.049, "end": 80.349, "zh": "我不会这么做的。", "zh_hant": "我不會這麼做的。"}, {"index": 33, "text": "Yeah it was hard.", "start": 79.949, "end": 81.529, "zh": "是啊，那时候真的很难。", "zh_hant": "是啊，那時候真的很難。"}, {"index": 34, "text": "Do you have moments now where you have a dongsaeng and you're like, hey.", "start": 81.129, "end": 84.19, "zh": "那你现在有dongsaeng的时候，会不会也这样对她们？", "zh_hant": "那你現在有dongsaeng的時候，會不會也這樣對她們？"}, {"index": 35, "text": "I never do that.", "start": 84.57, "end": 85.55, "zh": "我从来不那样。", "zh_hant": "我從來不那樣。"}, {"index": 36, "text": "You don't do that?", "start": 85.15, "end": 86.11, "zh": "你不那样吗？", "zh_hant": "你不那樣嗎？"}, {"index": 37, "text": "I never do that.", "start": 85.71, "end": 86.49, "zh": "我从来不那样。", "zh_hant": "我從來不那樣。"}, {"index": 38, "text": "Because everybody's chingu.", "start": 86.09, "end": 87.511, "zh": "因为大家都是chingu。", "zh_hant": "因為大家都是chingu。"}, {"index": 39, "text": "Yes.", "start": 87.391, "end": 88.051, "zh": "对。", "zh_hant": "對。"}, {"index": 40, "text": "Everybody's chingu.", "start": 87.651, "end": 88.891, "zh": "大家都是朋友。", "zh_hant": "大家都是朋友。"}, {"index": 41, "text": "Okay.", "start": 88.751, "end": 89.491, "zh": "好的。", "zh_hant": "好的。"}, {"index": 42, "text": "That's good.", "start": 89.411, "end": 90.231, "zh": "这样很好。", "zh_hant": "這樣很好。"}, {"index": 43, "text": "I'm that kind of style.", "start": 89.831, "end": 91.172, "zh": "我就是那种风格。", "zh_hant": "我就是那種風格。"}, {"index": 44, "text": "That's good.", "start": 91.272, "end": 93.072, "zh": "这样很好。", "zh_hant": "這樣很好。"}, {"index": 45, "text": "But…", "start": 92.672, "end": 93.232, "zh": "但是……", "zh_hant": "但是……"}, {"index": 46, "text": "Okay.", "start": 92.832, "end": 93.772, "zh": "好吧。", "zh_hant": "好吧。"}, {"index": 47, "text": "I'm kind of kkondae.", "start": 93.372, "end": 94.672, "zh": "我算是有点kkondae。", "zh_hant": "我算是有點kkondae。"}, {"index": 48, "text": "Sorry.", "start": 95.413, "end": 96.973, "zh": "抱歉。", "zh_hant": "抱歉。"}, {"index": 49, "text": "I was like…", "start": 96.573, "end": 97.353, "zh": "我当时就想……", "zh_hant": "我當時就想……"}, {"index": 50, "text": "The first time I met him, he was like…", "start": 96.953, "end": 98.693, "zh": "我第一次见到他的时候，他说……", "zh_hant": "我第一次見到他的時候，他說……"}, {"index": 51, "text": "I'm Bonnie.", "start": 99.354, "end": 100.434, "zh": "我是Bonnie。", "zh_hant": "我是Bonnie。"}, {"index": 52, "text": "Hello.", "start": 100.474, "end": 101.194, "zh": "你好。", "zh_hant": "你好。"}]